---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import CTA from '../../components/CTA.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Pusher Type Furnace Accessories For Sequential Processing" description="You require robust components for high-capacity pusher systems. Our specialized furnace parts provide reliable performance in sequential heat treatment lines.">
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <p class="text-orange-600 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-sm mb-4">Furnace Application Solutions</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-blue-900 mb-8 leading-tight">Pusher Type Furnace Accessories For Sequential Processing</h1>
      
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-600 mb-12">
        <p>You require robust components that can withstand the mechanical pushing force and thermal gradients of sequential heat treatment lines. Our specialized furnace parts are engineered to provide reliable performance in the demanding environments of high-capacity pusher systems. You ensure consistent carburizing or hardening results for your automotive and industrial parts by utilizing our precision-manufactured atmosphere control and temperature measurement accessories.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-16">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-4">The Technical Challenge</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Pusher furnaces often experience atmosphere contamination between zones. You need precise flow control and probe monitoring for each stage.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-4">The Weigu Solution</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Weigu provides multi-zone monitoring kits and drip feeders. You maintain independent carbon potential in each zone, guaranteeing metallurgical precision.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <section class="bg-blue-900 text-white p-10 rounded-3xl shadow-xl">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Key Components For This Application</h2>
        <ul class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-orange-500">✔</span> Zone-Control Drip Kits</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-orange-500">✔</span> High-Temp Thermocouples</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-orange-500">✔</span> Casting Support Rails</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-orange-500">✔</span> Thermal Insulation Blankets</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <div class="mt-16">
        <CTA title="Optimize Your Pusher Furnace Process Today" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
